author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Rushia was taken by surprise... Not only received an amount of carrots... Also more alchemy (Potions), armor, flowers, a bed module, the "lost diamonds" and especially a new "tsurupettachi" (Special pickaxe diamond)

Bunny Goddess (Pekora-san, of course. That nickname was about her golden eyes, because normal bunnies have red eyes) noticed about falling accidents from 2 previous streams ago.

Thats why the 3rd Generation (Holofantasy) is the best generation ever.
Talking about it, I'm composing a song for my idol group "Kousei no Onpu" which also is a tribute to Holofantasy.

author: ะเนนรดก กเรรน
Amai Ta. Yume
text: Rushia, today was a wonderful experience from the beginning to the end. While I was doing the final work of the day,  your voice inspires me to do many things still. I took a lot of glances towards your Minecraft stream, seeing the creeper explode and thanking your fans again, I am so glad that I stayed for 5 hours. It was all worth it and not a waste of my life. It helps keep up my mental health as well and prove that I have something to watch more. Thank you for the hard work. Be safe there and we'll keep on supporting you. I'll do anything to help you when I have the chance! Thank you fandeads for your support to her. It was wholesome and amazing to see!
